---
title: Scenario 3 — Normal Add / Remove (Happy Path)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Service as Backend Service
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant Sub as Throttled Subscription
    participant Box as AnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant Containers as Container Pool

    Service->>Cache: AddOrUpdate(newItem)
    Sub-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Add) after 150ms

    Box->>Box: ClassifyChange\nHasAnyPendingReason() = false\ne.Action = Add\n→ ChangeType.AddRemove

    Box->>Pipeline: Enqueue AddRemove snapshot
    Note over Pipeline: AddRemove is never collapsed\nEach one is preserved

    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext\n_pipelineBusy = true
    Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(AddRemove)
    Box->>Box: OnBeforeAnimatedDiff() — no-op in base class

    Box->>Box: DiffVisible(desired)\nNewItem not in VisibleItems\nVisibleItems.Insert(idx, newItem)

    Box->>Containers: PrepareContainerForItemOverride
    Containers->>Containers: Cancel prior animation (none)\nResetVisuals() — snap to neutral
    Containers->>Box: ConsumeEntryReason(id)
    Note over Containers: No stamp → EntryReason.Default
    Containers->>Containers: RunFade(0 → 1, EntryDuration)\nOpacity animates in

    Containers->>Containers: _inflightCount++

    Note over Containers: 200ms fade plays

    Containers->>Containers: Animation complete\nOpacity snapped to 1\n_inflightCount--

    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false

    Note over Box: --- REMOVE SCENARIO ---

    Service->>Cache: Remove(existingItem)
    Sub-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Remove) after 150ms

    Box->>Pipeline: Enqueue AddRemove snapshot
    Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot
    Box->>Box: DiffVisible\nItem in VisibleItems, not in desired\nnot in _activeExits\nBeginExit(item)

    Box->>Box: ConsumeExitReason(id)
    Note over Box: No stamp → ExitReason.Default
    Box->>Box: RunFade(1 → 0, ExitDuration)\nItem stays in VisibleItems as ghost

    Box->>Box: _inflightCount++

    Note over Box: 200ms fade plays\nItem visible but fading

    Box->>Box: Animation complete\n_activeExits.ContainsKey(id) = true\n_activeExits.Remove(id)\nVisibleItems.RemoveAt(IndexOfById(id))\n_inflightCount--

    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
